tilted his head quizzically as he looked at TUCSON and then nodded,
humor glinting in his eye. &quot;I do not come for your progeny.&quot; he said
as he straightened. &quot;There is one who would speak with you.&quot;

As DISCIPLE spoke the other dragons were still bowing or at least
looking down deferentially. A few whispered the name ARCANE in hushed
